Numora is a simple and clean Android calculator app built using Kotlin in Android Studio. It allows users to perform basic arithmetic operations with a smooth and minimal user interface.

Features
Basic arithmetic operations (+, −, ×, ÷)
Clean and simple UI
Backspace support
Real-time input display
Error handling for invalid input
Fast and lightweight performance
Tech Stack
Kotlin
Android Studio
XML (UI Design)
Android SDK
How It Works
User enters numbers and operators using buttons
Expression is displayed on screen
Pressing "=" evaluates the expression and shows result
Backspace removes last entered character
Future Improvements
Scientific calculator mode
History of calculations
Dark mode support
More advanced expression parsing
